{"tid":2443350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英籍老師不獲發工作簽証，好似話好多老師都有呢個情況","createTime":"2021-03-12T04:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T07:51:46.000Z","uid":261647,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"c2c560fc4c7c060eed7e4e92d1f51e08119dd62a","tid":2443350,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:26:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jaiszechi.chan/posts/10157917361962187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjaiszechi.chan%2Fposts%2F10157917361962187&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw1znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=0139bca2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jaiszechi.chan/posts/10157917361962187</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：Jai Sze Chi Chan<br />\n<br />\n英籍老師不獲發工作簽証，好似話好多國際學校老師都有呢個情況<br />\n<br />\n剛收到，from：康怡 Steps Education<br />\nDear parents,<br />\nWe are very sorry that the visa of Ms Maddie was rejected by Immigration last Monday and Immigration requires her to leave HK in 10 days.<br />\nThroughout the years, we have always succeeded in getting the visa of every single teacher. However, out of a huge shock, Ms Maddie&rsquo;s visa extension was rejected with the reason that the unemployment rate in Hong Kong is historically high and a NET is not a must to teach English classes.<br />\nI would like to call for your understanding that we have never experienced such before. We also heard that many international schools in Hong Kong encountered similar problems lately, especially on the visa of UK teachers.<br />\nWe have been trying our best to extend Ms Maddie&rsquo;s period of stay in Hong Kong so as to facilitate better with the teacher transition in Steps. However, the Immigration Department still does not allow Ms Maddie to stay in HK to wait for the visa appeal results"},{"pid":"0ebc9a637621635495626c4067a26e984a8ed482","tid":2443350,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse